      <section eId="sec_CHC-1267">
        <num>CHC 1267</num>
        <heading>1267.  Burden of proof</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1267__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>That they have been unreasonably denied visitation rights.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1267__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>That limited visitation rights would be in the best interest of the child.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
